about.summary: A dot-accessible dictionary (a la JavaScript objects).

name: munch
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "2.0.4" %}

package:
  name: munch
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: munch-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/Infinidat/munch/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ec4f073cc6437787383a44f5e70148469abbc6123bc8798cd2443e7c5361c8ab

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - munch

about:
  home: http://github.com/Infinidat/munch
  license: MIT
  summary: 'A dot-accessible dictionary (a la JavaScript objects).'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
